               <msContents>
                  <summary>Miniature Codex of Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡  and Asmat Prayers</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="26r" to="38r" facs="026">Fols 26r–38r, </locus>
                     <locus from="1r" to="15r" facs="001">1r–15r</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <note>incomplete at the beginning</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="15r" to="20r" facs="015">Fols 15r–20r</locus>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5876AsmatPrayer">Asmat Prayer of the Archangel Mika’el.  Cf. Asmat Prayer of the Archangel Mika’el which is written on his left and right wings. Often included in Dersana Michael in the month of Ḫǝdar</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ቃላተ፡ እግዚእብሔር ይቀጠቅጥ፡ ፀብዓ፡ ወእግዚአብሔር፡ ስሙ፡ ኤኮስ፡ አስሊ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="20r" to="22v" facs="020">Fols 20r–22v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer for Binding the demon, Cf. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕሠረ፡ አጋንንት፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕሠሩ፡ ለጋኔን፡</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="22v" to="24v" facs="023">Fols 22v–24v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Evil Eye, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓይነ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓይነ፡ ጽላ፡ ዓይነ፡ ሰብእ፡ እኩያን፡ አጋንንት፡ ጸዋጋን፡ ዓይነ፡ ደስክ፡ ሕሱማን፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
